{
    "_comment": [
        "QuickDASH: Quick Disabilities of the Arm, Shoulder and Hand",
        "上肢障害簡易評価票",
        "原典: Beaton DE, Wright JG, Katz JN; Upper Extremity Collaborative Group. Development of the QuickDASH: comparison of three item-reduction approaches. J Bone Joint Surg Am. 2005;87(5):1038-1046.",
        "公式サイト: https://dash.iwh.on.ca/about-quickdash",
        "著作権: Institute for Work & Health",
        "評価方式: 各項目1-5点、0-100点スケールに変換",
        "計算式: QuickDASHスコア = ((合計点 / 11) - 1) × 25"
    ],
    "title": "QuickDASH上肢障害簡易評価票",
    "description": [
        "過去1週間の上肢の状態について、以下の質問にお答えください。",
        "各質問について、最もあてはまるものを1つ選んでください。"
    ],
    "contact": "整形外科外来",
    "fields": [
        {
            "dispname": "身体機能",
            "type": "subsection"
        },
        {
            "dispname": "重いドアを開ける",
            "name": "Q1",
            "type": "radio",
            "required": true,
            "selector": [
                "困難なし",
                "やや困難",
                "中等度困難",
                "かなり困難",
                "できない"
            ],
            "selectoridx": "1|2|3|4|5"
        },
        {
